value.string: White sandy BEACHFRONT Makena, Maui elegantly furnished turn-key residential condominium with gated entry, and private sport court. Ideal for the discerning Buyer desiring the comfort, luxury and privacy of a home with the convenience of a turn-key condominium inclusive of on-site concierge property manager services. Spacious 4 bedroom 4.5 bath private residence situated on 12,996 sf. of land, large covered lanai to enjoy the Maui lifestyle, fire pit, private pool, spa, built-in barbecue, wet bar, water features, bocce ball court & security system . Amenities include high wood inlayed ceilings, stone flooring, billiard room, wine room, fireplace, office, gourmet kitchen, central A/C, reverse osmosis water system and electronic window coverings throughout. Makena is considered by most to be the most exclusive area on Maui with the finest ocean activities. Only minutes to the Shops at Wailea and fine dining! Also listed as Condo. See MLS# 349475

Perfect Waterman's location. A cement/stucco well built home. Less than a mile from Baldwin Beach, 3 mi. to Hookipa and just a bike ride to Paia. A quaint beach community surrounds the home and is walking distance to the North Shore's famous Baby Beach. This 4 bedroom, 3 bath, two car garage with an Italian Stucco style "Great Room", now being used as a gym, sits on the Maui Country Club Course with unobstructed views to the trees of Baby Beach. Raising kids is easy and fun in this quiet neighborhood. The location is only minutes from highly accredited schools and amenities. Must see to understand the unique lifestyle this home offers. Listor/owner holds active Real Estate License in the State of Hawaii, and is related to other owner.
